CardClearingProcedure	retrieve	Retrieve details about a card clearing process		retrieveCardClearingProcedure		#desc
Capture	update	Update details of a captured card transaction (for repair)	updateCardClearingProcedureCapture	updateCardClearingProcedureCapture		Update to any amendable fields of the Capture instance
