Fees	update	Update details of applied fees	updateCardClearingProcedureFees	updateCardClearingProcedureFees		Update to any amendable fields of the Fees instance
Fees	retrieve	Retrieve details about card transaction intercharge fees	retrieveCardClearingProcedureFees	retrieveCardClearingProcedureFees		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Fees instance related report
Matching	retrieve	Retrieve details about card transaction matching	retrieveCardClearingProcedureMatching	retrieveCardClearingProcedureMatching		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Matching instance related report
Reconciliation	retrieve	Retrieve details about card transaction reconciliation	retrieveCardClearingProcedureReconciliation	retrieveCardClearingProcedureReconciliation		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Reconciliation instance related report
Routing	retrieve	Retrieve details about card transaction routing	retrieveCardClearingProcedureRouting	retrieveCardClearingProcedureRouting		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Routing instance related report
